name: "back in black(and in LA)"

Ricardus
Ricardus is the fusion between Ricardo Fort & Frida Kahlo, each edition can also have a shout out to other iconic celebrities.
after some adventures with gloomtube it seems that ricardus was possessed by Hedi Xandt's art, we don't know what happened to him, the only clue is that he might be back in LA, if we go by his Kobe jersey.
